    "### Encapsulation \n",
    "    -> Encapsulation means binding data and methods togehter and restricitng direct access.\n",
    "    Data + Protection\n",
    " --- \n",
    " There are three types of variables:\n",
    "- Private\n",
    "- Public\n",
    "- Protected\n"
   ]
  },
