    "- Logical hierarchy\n",
    "- Less repition\n",
    "Example:\n",
    "    Parent -> Child\n",
    "    Vehicale -> car, Bike\n",
    "Syntax -> Class ChildClass(ParentClass):\n",
    "\n",
    "1) Single Level Inheritance\n",
    "One Parent Class -> One Child Class\n",
    "Example: Animal -> Dog\n",
    "\n",
    "- Parent CLass, SuperClass\n",
    "- Child CLass, SubClass\n",
    "\n"
   ]
